name: node-zanarkand-proto
description: A wrapper for acchan's Zanarkand network capture library.

scripts.unfirewall7: netsh advfirewall firewall add rule name="ZanarkandWrapperJSON" dir=in action=allow program=./Zanarkand/ZanarkandWrapperJSON.exe enable=yes
scripts.unfirewallXP: netsh firewall set allowedprogram ./Zanarkand/ZanarkandWrapperJSON.exe ZanarkandWrapperJSON ENABLE

author: karashiiro
